<pb n="00"/><p rend="center">śrīparamātmane namaḥ |</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">sanātanajainagraṃthamālāyāḥ</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">prathamaṃ khaṃḍaṃ |</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">syādvādavidyāpatiśrīmadvidyānaṃdasvāmiviracitā</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">1</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">āptaparīkṣā</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">2</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">patraparīkṣā ca</p>

<lb/><p rend="center">śrīyutapaṃḍitagajādharalālajainaśāstriṇā saṃpādite</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">te ca</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">usmānāvādanivāsisvargīyaśreṣṭhivaryakastūracaṃdrasyātmajabālacaṃdrasyasmaraṇārthaṃ</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">śrījainadharmapracāriṇīsabhāyāmaṃtriṇā</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">śrīpannālālajainena</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">kāśīsthacaṃdraprabhānāmnimudraṇayaṃtrālaye</p>
<lb/><p rend="center">prakāśite |</p>
