<pb n="01"/><head rend="bc">śrīparamātmane namaḥ | <lb/>sanātanajainagraṃthamālā | <lb/> 2 <lb/>syādvādavidyāpatiśrīvidyānaṃdasvāmiviracitā <lb/>patraparīkṣā</head>
<lb/><lg><l>śrīvarddhamānamānutya syādvādanyāyanāyakaṃ |</l>
<lb/><l>prabuddhāśeṣatattvārthaṃ patravākyaṃ vicā1ryate ||1||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>kasmātpunaḥ śrīvarddhamānamarhaṃtaṃ bhagavaṃ taṃsyādvādanyāyanāyakaṃ prakarṣeṇasākṣādbuddhāśeṣadravyaparyāyātmajīvā-
<lb/>dipadārthamevānutya patravākyamācāryaparaṃparayā vica2ratvicāryate | nanvakṣapādādyekāṃtavādināmanyatamamityatrocyate|</p>
<lb/><lg><l>naikāṃtavādināṃ patravākyaṃ saṃbhavadarthakaṃ | ta3ttattvā4dhiga5mopāyaprakāśarahitatvataḥ ||1||</l>
<lb/><l>yattu saṃbhavadarthātmā na tattādṛkṣamīkṣitaṃ | yathāsyādvādabhṛdvākyaṃ6 tadṛkvedaṃ na ta7ttathā8 ||2||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>nanvakṣapādādīnāṃ patravākyaṃ tāvannetyayuktaṃ tasyaprasiddhāvayavatvena prasiddhatvāt devadattādivā9kyavat
<lb/>nāpi tadasaṃbhavadarthakaṃ sveṣṭasyārthasya sādhakatvāt |na cā'sādhugūḍhapadaprāyamapi patramāsajyate sādhugūḍhapadaprā-
<lb/>yasyaiva nirākulasya tasya tairāveditatvāt | taducyate--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>prasiddhāvayavaṃ vākyaṃ sveṣṭasyārthasya sādhakaṃ | sādhugūḍhapadaprāyaṃ patramāhuranāku10laṃ ||1||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>kathaṃ punaḥ prasiddhāvayavatvādiviśeṣaṇaviśiṣṭaṃ vākyaṃpatraṃ nāma tasya śru11tipathasamadhigamyapadasamudāya-
<lb/>viśeṣarūpatvāt patrasya tadviparītākāratvāt na cayadyato'nyattattena vyapadiśyate'tiprasaṃgāt nīlādayopi 
<lb/>hikaṃbalādibhyo'nye na te nīlā12divyapadeśahetavaḥ teṣāṃtadya13padeśahetutayā pratīyamānatvāt kirīṭādīnāṃ 
<lb/>pṛruṣetadvyapadeśahetutvavat tadyogāttatra matvarthīyavidhānāt |nīlādayaḥ saṃti yeṣāṃ te nīlādayaḥ kaṃbalādaya iti
<lb/>guṇavacanebhyo matvarthīyasyābhāvaprasiddheriticetupacaritopacārāditi kramaḥ | śrotrapathaprasthāyino hi śabdā-
<lb/>tmakasya padasamudāyaviśeṣarūpasya lipyāmu14pacāraḥ tatratasya15 janairāropyamāṇatvāt lipyupacaritavākyasyāpi 
<lb/>patresamupacaryamāṇatvāt tatra likhitasya patrasthatvāttadupacaritopacārāt patravyapadeśasiddheḥ na ca yadyato
<lb/>'nyattattenopacārādupacāropacārāt vā vyapadeṣṭumaśakyaṃśakrāda16nyatra vya17vahartṛjane śakrābhiprāye sphuṭamupacāra-
<lb/>darśanāt tato'nyatrāpi kā18ṣṭādāvupacāropacārātśakravyapadeśasiddheḥ taduktaṃ--
<lb/><seg type="note-block-page-foot">1 svābhāvikameva | 2 āgacchat | 3 teṣāṃ | 4 jīvāditattva- |5 svārthaniścayasya | 6 pramāṇanayapradarśakavākyaṃ | 
<lb/>7 tasmāt | 8 saṃbhavadarthātmaiva | 9 ādiśabdena gāmānaya śuklāṃdaṃḍenetyādigrahaṇaṃ | 10 doṣai rahitaṃ | 11 karṇa | 12
<lb/>nīlaḥ kaṃbala ityatra kaṃbalohyanena nīlena vyapadiśyateityata āha | 13 teṣu kaṃbalādiṣu nīlādivyapadeśahetavo nabhavaṃtī- 
<lb/>tyarthaḥ | 14 lipireva vākyamiti | 15 vākyasya| 16 bhinne | 17 paṃḍitādau | 18 ādiśabdena pāṣāṇādigrahaṇaṃ |</seg></p>
<pb n="02"/><lg><l>mukhyaṃ śa1bdātmakaṃ vākyaṃ lipyāmāropyate janaiḥ| patrasthatvāttu tatpatramupacāropacārataḥ ||1||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>athavā prakṛtavākyasya mukhyata eva patravyapadeśa itiniga2dāmaḥ padāni trāyaṃte gopyaṃte rakṣyaṃte parebhyaḥ
<lb/>prativādibhyaḥ svayaṃ vijigīṣuṇā yasmin vākye tatpatramitipatraśabdasya nirvacanasiddheḥ | tathā loke 
<lb/>vyavaharttariśāstre ca gu3ruparvakramāyāte pratīteḥ na ca padāniviniścitapadasvarūpatadabhidheyatattvebhyaḥ parebhya-
<lb/>strātumaśakyānyeva kutaścidvarṇaviparyāsanādeḥprakṛtipratyayādigopanādvā tattrāṇasaṃbhavātpadagūḍhādikāvyavattaduktaṃ--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>trāyaṃte vā padānyasminparebhyo vijigīṣuṇā | kutaściditipatraṃ syālloke śāstre ca rūḍhitaḥ ||2||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>na caivamasādhupadāspadamapi vākyaṃ patramāsajyatesuspaṣṭapadameva vā sādhugūḍhapadaprāyamitivacanāttaduktaṃ--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>nacāsādhupadaṃ vākyaṃ praspaṣṭapadameva vā |sādhugūḍhapadaprāyamiti tasya viśeṣaṇāt ||3||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>padapādādigūḍhakāvyamevaṃ patraṃ prāpnoti iti cennaprasiddhāvayavatvena viśiṣṭa4sya patratvavacanāt na hipadagūḍhādikāvyaṃ
<lb/>pramāṇasiddhapratijñādyavayavaviśeṣaṇatayākiṃcitprasiddhaṃ tasya tathā prasiddhaupatravyapadeśasiddheravādhitatvāttaduktaṃ--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>padagūḍhādikāvyaṃ ca naivaṃ patraṃ prasajyate |prasiddhāvayavatvena viśiṣṭasyābhidhā5nataḥ ||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>sva6yamiṣṭasyārthasyāsādhakamapi tādṛ7gvākyaṃpatramevamāsaktamiti cenna sveṣṭārthasādhanasyaivehapatravicāre patratva- 
<lb/>vacanāt tadapya8bhihitaṃ--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>sveṣṭhārthāsādhanasyāpi naivaṃ patratva9māpatet |sveṣṭārthasādhanasyaiva patratvavacanādiha ||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>tato nākṣapādādīnāmekāṃtavādināṃpatravākyamasaṃbhavadarthakaṃ iti kecittadasatyathoktalakṣaṇasya patra- 
<lb/>vākyasya teṣāṃvicāryamāṇasyāvyavasthiteḥ tathā10hi--nākṣapādasyatāvadyathoktalakṣaṇaṃ patravākyaṃ saṃbhavati prasi-
<lb/>ddhāvayavatvasya virahātsugatādīnāmiva | tadavayavāhipratijñā11dayaḥ paṃcākṣapādenābhidhīyaṃtepratijñāhetūdāharaṇopa- 
<lb/>nayanigamanānyavayavā itisūtrapraṇayanāt | tatrāgamaḥ pratijñā viśvataścakṣu12ritiviśvato mu13kho viśvato bā14hu- 
<lb/>riti viśva15taḥ pātsaṃbāhu16bhyāṃ dhamati saṃpata17ttrairdyāvābhūmī janayandevaeka iti yathā āgamārtho vā pratijñā
<lb/>vivādādhyā18sitamupala19bdhimatkāraṇakamiti | yathāheturanumānaṃ tena pratijñātārthasyānumīyamānatvāt kāryatvāditi| 
<lb/>yathā udāharaṇaṃ pratyakṣaṃ vādiprativādinoryatrabuddhisāmyaṃ tadudāharaṇamiti vacanāt vastrādivaditi yathā
<lb/>upanayamupamānaṃ dṛṣṭāṃtaḥ dharmisādhyadharmiṇoḥ sādṛśyāt,"prasiddhasādharmyāt sādhyasādhanamupamānamiti" vacanāt
<lb/>yatkāryaṃ tadupalabdhimatkāraṇakaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ yathā vastrāditathā ca vivādādhyāsitamiti | yathāsarveṣā20mekaviṣayatvaprada- 
<lb/>rśanaphalaṃ nigamanaṃtasmā21dupalabdhimatkāraṇakamiti yathāāgamānumānapratyakṣopamānavat phalasamudāyarūpa-
<lb/>tvātpaṃcānāmavayavānāmiti vyākhyā22nāt | na caitepaṃcāvayavāḥ pramāṇato vicāryamāṇā vipaściccetasi suniści-
<lb/>tāścakāsati, patravākyābhāse'pi saṃbhavāt teṣāṃpakṣadharmatvasapakṣesatvavipakṣāsatvamātrāṇāmivatrayāṇāmavayavānāṃ 
<lb/>sugatasaṃmatānāṃ vītādīnāmivakapilavikalpitānāṃ tadabhāve'pi patravākyasya svārthasādhanasyadarśanāt 
<lb/>sādhyāvinābhāvaniyamaniścayalakṣaṇādeva hetoḥsādhyaprasiddheḥ taduktaṃ--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>na caivaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ patramakṣapādasya yujyate |prasiddhāvayavatvasya virahātsugatādivat ||1||</l>
<lb/><l>patrasyāvayavāḥ paṃca pratijñādaya ityasat |patrābhāse'pi sadbhāvātteṣāṃ trairūpamātravat ||2||</l>
<lb/><l>tadabhāve'pi patrasya svārthasādhanatekṣaṇāt | hetoḥsādhyāvinābhāvaniyamātmakato yathā ||3||</l>
<lb/><l>satsatsaditisaṃkṣepātsādhyasādhanadarśanaṃ | vyāptyāḥsāmarthyataḥ sarvanāmābhāve'pi niścitaṃ ||4||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>nanu ca yatkṛtakaṃ tadanityaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ yathā ghaṭa ityādausati sarvanāmaprayoge vyāptyā sādhyasādhanavacana-
<lb/><seg type="note-block-page-foot">1 padasamudāyātmakaṃ | 2 vayaṃ jaināḥ | 3 paraṃparā | 4 vākyasya | 5 patratvābhidhānāt | 6 vādiprativādibhyāṃ | 7
<lb/>prasiddhāvayavaṃ sādhugūḍhapadaprāyaṃ ca | 8 abhyadhāyi | 9 na prāpnoti | 10 tadeva vivṛṇoti | 11 dharmadhārmisamudāyaḥpratijñā | 
<lb/>12 sarvadarśitvāt | 13 sakalaśāstrapraṇetṛtvāt |14 sarvakartṛtvāt | 15 sarvagatatvāt | 16 puṇyapāpābhyāṃ | 17
<lb/>paramāṇubhiḥ | 18 kṣityādikaṃ | 19 buddhimatkāraṇakaṃ | 20 pratijñādyavayavānāṃ | 21 kāryatvāt | 22 pūrvotkasūtravyā-
<lb/>khyānāt |</seg>
<pb n="03"/>mupalabdhaṃ na punarasati yataḥ sa1tsadityatrasarvanāmaprayogābhāve'pi saṃkṣepatastatsiddhyetdharmiṇaścāvaca2namihā- 
<lb/>yuktaṃ agnira3tradhūmādityādiṣudharmivacanadarśanāditi kaścit so'pyanālocitavacanapathaḥsāmarthyādgamyamānasya 
<lb/>sarvanāmno prayogevirodha4vaidhuryāt paṃcāvayavavādinaḥsādharmyāvayavavyākhyānādarthatogamyamānānāṃ vaidharmyā-
<lb/>vayavānāmiva kvacidavaśyaṃ tatprayoge paṃcāvaya5vavacanenyūnatā6nuṣaṃgāt avayavavādināṃ bauddhānāṃ tryaṃśasya heto-
<lb/>rbhāṣaṇāt sāmarthyato gamyamānānāṃ pratijñādīnāmivatatpra7yoge svayamasādhanāṃgavacanasya nigrahādhikaraṇasya
<lb/>tairabhidhānāt tata eva dharmiṇo'pyavacanamitisaṃkṣiptapatravākyena viruddhyate tasyaparīkṣādakṣairakṣū8ṇatayopa- 
<lb/>lakṣitatvāttaduktaṃ--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>vaidharmyāvayavā yadvatpaṃcāvayavavādinaḥ |sādharmyāvayavākhyānādgamyaṃte'rthādabhāṣitāḥ ||1||</l>
<lb/><l>pratijñāyāśca keṣāṃciddhetostryaṃśa9sya bhāṣaṇāt |sāmarthyādgamyamānatvānna prayojyā yathaiva tu ||2||</l>
<lb/><l>tathā sāmarthyagamyatvātsarvanāmnopyabhāṣaṇaṃ |kvacidiṣṭaṃ parīkṣāyāṃ dakṣairddharmiṇa eva ca ||3||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>nanvevaṃ kvacidapi pratijñādiprayoge na syādvādināṃyuktarūpobhavet tasya sāmarthyādgamyamānatvātsarva-
<lb/>nāmavaditi na manīṣibhirmanasi nidheyaṃ teṣāṃpratipādyānurodhena prayogopagamāt yathaiva hikasyacitpratibo- 
<lb/>dhyasyānurodhena sādhanavākyesaṃdhā10bhidhīyate dṛṣṭāṃ11tādikamapi na caivaṃsādhanasyaikala12kṣaṇatvaṃ sva13yaṃ parīkṣita-
<lb/>mapakṣipyate tato'nyāṃśānāṃ satāmapitallakṣaṇatvāpāyātsādhanābhāsepitatsaṃbhavāda14sādhāraṇatāvirahāt ta15thaiva 
<lb/>hikumāranaṃdibhaṭṭārakairapi svavādanyāyenigaditatvāttadāha--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>pratipādyānurodhena prayogeṣu punaryathā | pratijñāprocyate tajjñaistathodāharaṇādikaṃ ||1||</l>
<lb/><l>na caivaṃ sādhanasyaikalakṣaṇatvaṃ virudhyate |hetulakṣaṇatāpāyādanyāṃśasya ta16thoditaṃ ||2||</l>
<lb/><l>anyathānupapattyekalakṣaṇaṃ liṃga17maṃgyate |prayogaparipāṭī tu pratipādyānurodhataḥ ||3||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>nanu cātisaṃkṣiptapatravākye hetureva prayoktavyaḥtāvanmātrātsādhyamavaboddhuṃ samarthān narānprati sādhyā-
<lb/>bhidhānasya nirarthakatvāt prapaṃcatāratamyāt sādhyaṃniścetumī18śān prati dvau cāvayavau prayoktavyau pakṣohetuśceti 
<lb/>trayaścāvayavāḥ kāṃ19ścana pratipakṣoheturdṛṣṭāṃtaśceti | catvāro vā20 taevāvayavāḥsopanayāḥ parānugrahapravaṇaiḥ 
<lb/>sadbhiḥ prayoktavyāḥ |paṃca vā21 pratijñāhetūdāharaṇopanayanigamanabhedāt |a22nyathā tatpratipatterayogāditya23nye 
<lb/>prāhuḥ tadāha--</p>
<lb/><lg><l>hetureva prayoktavyastāvanmātrātpravedituṃ |sama24rthānpratibodhyān nṝn sādhyaṃ saṃkṣepato na25nu ||1||</l>
<lb/><l>dvau ca trayaśca catvāraḥ paṃca cāvayavāḥ pare |prayoktavyāḥ pra26paṃcena sadbhirityapare viduḥ ||2||</l></lg>
<lb/><p>te'pyevaṃ pṛṣṭavyāḥ hetustāvatkeva27laḥ prayujyamānaḥkathaṃ prayujyata iti yadi prathamāṃtaḥ satsadityeva
<lb/>tadāsya kutaḥ sādhyatvavya28vacchedaḥsādhyalakṣaṇavaikalyāt satsattvasya prasiddhatvātsādhyasyāprasiddhalakṣaṇatvāt kiṃ 
<lb/>punaḥ satsadityucyateyatasta29tsakalajanaprasiddhaṃ sādhyavyavacchedenasādhanatvenaiva buddhyāmahe na punaḥ sādhyanirdeśa-
<lb/>tvena30 śaṃkāmahe sa31tsaditi cet i32me brūmahe sa33danaṃsaditi pramā ya34to'trā35bhipretā sarvairgatyarthatvātgatyarthasya ca
<lb/><seg type="note-block-page-foot">1 sarvamanekāṃtātmakamutpādavyayadhrauvyayuktaṃsatsatsatvādityarthaḥ | 2 apratipādanaṃ | 3 parvatādau nāmnaḥ| 4 virodha- 
<lb/>virodhāt | 5 sādharmyāvayavapaṃcakasyaivavacena | 6 hīnaṃ anyatamena nyūnamiti nigrahasthānānuṣaṃgāt | 7 yatra paṃcāvayava- 
<lb/>prayoge | 8 paripūrṇatayā | 9 pakṣadharmatvasapakṣesatvavipakṣādvyāvṛtirūpasya | 10 pratijñā saṃdhā pratijñāḥ, maryādetyamaraḥ | 11
<lb/>upanayanigamanayorgrahaṇaṃ | 12 iti parāśaṃkāṃ manasi kṛtvānirākṛtavān jainaḥ | 13 anyathānupapattiḥ | 14 pratijñādīnāṃ
<lb/>viśeṣarūpatvarahitatvāt | 15 tadeva vivṛṇoti | 16 pravakṣyamāṇaṃ varttate | 17 aṃgīkriyate | 18 jainānprati |19 sāṃkhyān 
<lb/>prati | 20 mīmāṃsakānprati | 21 yogānprati | 22 uktaviparyaye evaṃ na prayujyate cet | 23 saugatāḥ | 24 prapaṃcena 
<lb/>sādhyaṃ pravedituṃ samarthān nṝn prati | 25 aho | 26 prameyāṃtaḥ | 27 kena prakāreṇa | 28 vyāvṛtiḥ | 29 satsaditiliṃgaṃ 
<lb/>30 pratipādanatvena | 31 satsadititaddheturityarthaḥ | 32 bauddhāḥ | 33 yuṭ pratyayo'trajñātavyaḥ | 34 kāraṇāt | 
<lb/>35 anumāne |</seg>
<pb n="04"/>jñānārthatvātsarve gatyarthā jñānārthe varttaṃte itivacanātsatī vidyamānā sā ya1smin tatsatsadvidyamānapramaṃprameyamiti 
<lb/>yāvanna kasyacitpramāṇavādinaḥprameyamaprasiddhaṃ | saṃvitamātrapramāṇavādinaḥtadaprasiddhamiti na maṃtavyaṃ tasyāpi 
<lb/>saṃvitsvarūpeprameyatvaprasiddheḥ svarūpasya svato gatiritisvayamabhidhānātsaṃvṛ2tyā tadabhidhāne paramārthataḥ svarū-
<lb/>pādigativirodhātsaṃvidadvaitasiddherayogāt | yadipunarutpādā3disvabhāvatvaṃ satvaṃ tadā tatsatsatsādhyamitiyuktaṃ 
<lb/>vidya4mānotpādādisvabhāvatvasya satsattvasyakeṣāṃcidaprasiddhatvāt sādhyalakṣaṇasaṃpratipatterityevaṃye bru5vaṃte teṣāṃ 
<lb/>satsadityukte satsatvasya prasiddhatayāsādhyavya6vacchedasiddhāvapi sādhanasya dharmiṇo vyavacchedaḥsiddhyet tasyāpi 
<lb/>prasiddhatvena saṃma7tatvātprasiddhodharmīti vacanāt yadi pu8narviduṣāṃsādhyasiddhyarthaṃ dharmiṇo prayojyatvāttasya
<lb/>sādhyāvinā9bhāvābhāvādeva vyavacchedasiddhiriti mataṃtadā hetuḥ kevalaḥ kathaṃ teṣāṃ prayojyaḥ syāt sveṣṭasi-
