<pb n="07"/>pratīteḥ na punaḥ pradhvaṃsābhāvasya tadabhāvāditimataṃ tadā kathaṃcitsattā1ditādatmyāt sattādivya2vahāro ghaṭa-
<lb/>paṭayoriti naikāṃ3tena satvādi tato bhinnaṃ yenasaddravyā4tmanā ghaṭapaṭayorabhedaḥkathaṃcidabhinnapratibhāsatvaṃ vā na 
<lb/>syātsādhyasādhanavaikalyaṃ vā dṛṣṭāṃtasya tato nadravyaparyāyorbhedaikāṃtasādhanaṃ niravadyamasti yatasta5yoḥpa6dārthaṃ- 
