<lb/>nacāyamanaikāṃtiko viruddho vā sarvadā vipakṣevṛttyabhāvāt iti siddhatyevāto hetoḥkathaṃciddravyaparyāyayoraikyaṃ 
<lb/>tathā"dravyaparyāyayorekyaṃ pariṇā8maviśeṣāt yayostu naikyaṃ natayoḥ pariṇāmaviśeṣaḥ, yathā sahyaviṃdhyayoḥ
