<lb/>tathādravyaparyāyayoḥ kathaṃcidaikyaṃ śaktimacchaktibhāvāt yayostunaikyaṃ na tayoḥ śaktimacchaktibhāvaḥ yathā 
<lb/>sahyavindhyayoḥśaktimacchaktibhāvaśca dravyaparyāyayoriti vyatirekīheturanyathānupapattilakṣaṇaḥ sādhyaṃ sādhayati |
